It would have carried onto hit the stumps but the impact was the issue

commentary: de Silva to Chatara, OUT hat-trick on debut. Incredible scenes here at Galle. Hasaranga's team-mates run up to him, mob him, vigorously ruffle his air. Overflow of joy in the Sri Lankan camp. This is another googly,the perfect delivery to a tailender. This one pitches even wider outside off. Chatara sticks the bat out, does not move the feet at all, he is stapled to the crease as he pokes at it. Ends up leaving a daylight between bat and pad and the ball crashes into the stumps
